The music of the film composed by [[G. K. Venkatesh]] with lyrics for the soundtrack penned by [[Chi. Udaya Shankar]]. The song "If You Come Today" sung by [[Rajkumar (actor)|Rajkumar]] became widely popular, as the song was entirely written in unintentionally broken [[English language|English]].<ref>{{cite web |title= When Rajkumar sang... |url= http://www.rediff.com/movies/2006/apr/20rk.htm |publisher= ''[[Rediff.com]]'' |date= 20 April 2006 |accessdate= 2 May 2014}}</ref>

