== Re-release ==
''Operation Diamond Racket'' was re-released across 40 theatres in [[Karnataka]] on 31 May 2013.<ref name="toi" /> The film received a good opening, having collected {{INRConvert|1|l}} on the opening day in Kapali Theatre, [[Bangalore]].

